0.1.1.name: wordpress/spaceface-and-the-rest
0.1.1.description:
There are similar plugins but not one does what needed to syndicate and update your activities from providers like MySpace, YouTube, FaceBook etc.

After you register your FaceBook application, you can publish posts from your site to FaceBook by simply tagging your posts (supports title, body and image).

Also, now you can quickly update status mood on MySpace from SpaceFace->MySpace admin page.

Features

  • MySpace statuses display
  • MySpace activities display
  • MySpace videos display
  • MySpace status mood quick update from SpaceFace->MySpace admin page
  • YouTube favorites display as player or thumbnails
  • YouTube playlist as player or list that opens player in pop-up
  • FaceBook publishing from your site (supports title, body and image)
